    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071440/extras/366581f384f8f3f22e689a373083ee94.avif?t=1770959657\" width=600 height=92 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你这只新搬来世界上最友善最敦亲睦邻城市的长颈鹿，能在避开与任何人交谈的情况下，成功度过一周吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >长颈鹿有着自得其乐的生活，他喜欢听lo-fi音乐、喝抹茶、照顾自己的肉植，以及写写诗。但唯独有一件事为他的生活添增许多难关：任何社交场合都会令他社恐发作，如果还得跟人谈话，他的脑袋更是会原地爆炸。还好长颈鹿的隐藏存在感技能越来越强，满级的声东击西与秦王绕柱技能，让他成功避开与友好话痨的友善城（高票当选全球最友善城市！）居民对话。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们Quail button公司很荣幸发布《社恐长颈鹿的一周》这一款点击式潜行解谜游戏，你的任务就是要避开让任何人与你搭上话。随着你协助长颈鹿完成各种代办事务清单，你也将体验他丰富的一周生活，比如去洗衣店洗衣、去古董店淘宝贝，超市买菜，去健身房锻炼等等。与此同时还得如特工一样，成功避开超友好居民的攀谈，解开自己脑袋爆炸的重大危机！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071440/extras/3c17a717fa3cfe68f1ff2eca4b8716ff.poster.avif?t=1770959657\" width=600 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071440/extras/3c17a717fa3cfe68f1ff2eca4b8716ff.webm?t=1770959657\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071440/extras/3c17a717fa3cfe68f1ff2eca4b8716ff.mp4?t=1770959657\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071440/extras/7001ed577169a6c0246767faff87f5b4.avif?t=1770959657\" width=600 height=92 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一个使出需要三十六计来避免任何社交，与世上第一友好的居民们斗智斗勇来守护自己宁静生活的大冒险故事。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在无数个每周代办事件任务关卡中，有着令人会心一笑的幽默故事线，与潜行游戏的紧张刺激感的一款点击式冒险解谜游戏。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >友善城中各式各样的友好话痨居民都是你需要避开的噩梦。一旦搭上话，他们将十分乐意令你真正尸“首”分离。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >纯手绘画作与传统动画风格，为你呈现友善城的各方各面与多样化的居民，还有长颈鹿花式炸脑袋呢。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >将友善城各处融为一体的优美配乐，与令人放松的lo-fi音乐旋律。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071440/extras/982fba487c4914844574a232cb69c26c.webp?t=1770959657\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071440/extras/982fba487c4914844574a232cb69c26c.poster.avif?t=1770959657\" class=\"bb_img\" width=600 height=125 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
